uses%2F&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=398a3f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ef.com/wwen/english-resources/english-grammar/relative-clauses/</a>"},{"pid":"c39c9ca91c816fc2caf26bedd4400e5be316da44","tid":1047617,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"諗唔到用咩字駁住下一句就用"},{"pid":"80ef4bc1e05036ba85beca481d5457809b6735af","tid":1047617,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"fuck that, I am done with this shit"},{"pid":"52ef562a46db57bf534e1ff292b7868d34c88a41","tid":1047617,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"定係你想問幾時先要加個 &quot;,&quot;?"},{"pid":"f24e2ef791c174c8eef582ae6a9971c078c541dc","tid":1047617,"uid":215401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"fuck that shit"},{"pid":"c1f34bff8dde8ce11b3fd162b2d38ba28fd09f5e","tid":1047617,"uid":209999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"成班眼殘定理解能力有事 <br />\n佢問，後面加that"},{"pid":"bb2545a30fd582b5a8e2f7dc0d9b544fab9bae27","tid":1047617,"uid":1095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"that 前面唔會有 &lsquo;,&rsquo; <br />\n因為that係defining relative clause"},{"pid":"79e69532acfa5e71c7f7f2671d9f2377d9ae0eca","tid":1047617,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"名詞後加逗號，啫係你將會用一個名詞去解釋前面個名詞<br />\n咁如果你要用句子SVO去解釋之前個名詞<br />\n咁就要加個「果個」做代名詞<br />\n例如 that, which, who"},{"pid":"531a33f0ed110b5ca53dbc501fbc183bdf103aa2","tid":1047617,"uid":78460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"That-clause &ldquo;That&rdquo;後面跟完整clause (即係svo果d)<br />\neg. You know that I (s) love (v) you (o)<br />\n<br />\n我會咁睇 That-clause後面雖然係完整嘅clause 但係成舊嘢我會當佢名詞 &ldquo;That&rdquo;可以做subject或者object 而後面嘅嘢係補充個&rdquo;that&rdquo;嘅資訊<br />\n<br />\n記住一句句子<span style=\"color: red;\">只有一個main verb</span> that clause入面嘅並不是句子中嘅main verb<br />\n<br />\nI know that  &mdash;&gt;  I (s) know (v) that (o)<br />\n<br />\n呢個已經係一個完整句子 但係我想補充究竟我know乜嘢 我會用完整clause喺that後面補充<br />\n<br />\nI know <span style=\"color: red;\">that today is Monday</span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣睇嘅話其實成個that today is Monday係一個大嘅O<br />\n<br />\n你又可以當subject用<br />\n<br />\nThat I forgot to do my homework was very poor of me<br />\n<br />\n同樣地<br />\n<br />\nThat (s) was (v) very poor of me (c)<br />\n<br />\n我想補充That嘅資訊 我就加個clause入去<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;That I forgot to do my homework&rdquo;就變成一個大subject<br />\n<br />\n當然你亦可以好似relative clause (which xxx who xxx)果d咁用 去補充一個名詞嘅資訊<br />\n<br />\n就好似我地成日見嘅 <br />\nThe fact that there is nobody here is creepy<br />\n<br />\n呢度個subject係the fact 而個that-clause係補充&rdquo;the fact&rdquo;嘅資訊 <br />\n<br />\n記住一句句子只有一個main verb 好似上面呢句咁 出現左兩個is 但係前者喺that clause入面所以唔會係main verb <br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇句子最好搵咗main verb先 之後佢易睇好多 因為咁樣就可以搵到前面同後面嘅嘢 清楚係咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n利申: 憑記憶寫出嚟 有錯請改"},{"pid":"f975fff0d40b85bfff602d7d6b1b2314db63f375","tid":1047617,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"我諗你問緊嘅係relative clause入面嘅that點加逗號 <br />\n<br />\n答案好簡單: relative clause裡面嘅that永遠前面冇逗號 要加逗號嘅要用which<br />\n<br />\n但係注意relative clause有逗號同冇逗號意思會有少少分別喔"}]}